@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

title FIG-09-01. Online Store Delivery Decision Table

skinparam defaultFontSize 15

legend center
|= U |= Order value |= All items in stock? |= Destination |= Delivery decision |
| 1 | >= 50 | Yes | Domestic | Free standard delivery |
| 2 | < 50 | Yes | Domestic | Paid standard delivery |
| 3 | - | No | - | Stock exception review |
| 4 | - | Yes | International | Obtain international delivery quote |

DMN-style teaching table.
Hit policy U means Unique. The dash means any value.
The rules are non-overlapping within this simplified delivery example.
endlegend
@enduml
